  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink274-kilavi">varaiviṭai vaittup pirintuḻi āṟṟuvikkum tōḻikkut talaimakaḷ colliyatu.
          </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the heroine said to the confidante who consoles her when [the hero], having fixed the marriage, had separated.
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink274">
<l>mantik kaṇavaṉ kallāk kaṭuva</l>
<l>ṉoṇkēḻ vayappuli kuḻumaliṉ viraintuṭaṉ</l>
<l>kuṉṟuya raṭukkaṅ koḷḷu nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>ceṉṟaṉaṉ vāḻi tōḻiyeṉ</l>
<l>meṉṟōṭ kaviṉum pāyaluṅ koṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The man from the land where the uneducated male monkey,</l>
        <l>the husband of the female monkey,</l>
        <l>scampers at once</l>
        <l>at the roar of a strong tiger of gleaming lustre</l>
        <l>and takes hold of the high slopes of the hill—</l>
        <l>has gone, O friend,</l>
        <l>taking [with him]</l>
        <l>the beauty of [my] delicate shoulders</l>
        <l>and [my] sleep.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
